nhc_headline: ...COSME HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...COSME HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 8:00 AM MST Wed Jun 11 the center of Cosme was located near 16.4, -113.7 with movement ENE at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
